title: Freakshow Cakes
overview: Cooking Channel gets into the Halloween fun in Freakshow Cakes. In each episode of this one of-a-kind cake showdown, three of the most sinister cake artists step into a side-show tent to whip up the freakiest cakes imaginable. The baker who showcases the most wildly imaginative and hair-raising cake design wins $10,000 and the title of Freakshow Champion.
